testCases.content: Verify that when the registered player clicks the OG link/button, the request OG game launching URL should start
Verify that when the player does not have an account and clicks the OG link/button, the OG site should not launch
Verify that loading should start in 0 to 100%
A progress bar should be displayed along with the loading percentage
OG logo should display
Loading icon should remain centered
Animation and highlited UI loading icon should be removed
Loading should not revert to zero
After client loading OG game launching URL should display within 5 seconds
Goodtips labels should be correct
PRD-2225 - The promotion banner should not overlap with the other game tables
IDLING IN A DIFFERENT TAB AND THEN RETURNING TO THE OG LIVE TAB (PORTRAIT MODE)

Player should not receive a pop-up notification
for idling less than 10 minutes
Page should reload after clicking anywhere in the page
Player should be redirected in the lobby after the page is reloaded

Idling pop-up notification should not be displayed when the player is active
OG Live should be fully functional after being reloaded and redirected to the lobby due to idling.
